{"class":243},"-",[39,256,257],{"class":239},"on:pageService",[39,259,244],{"class":243},[39,261,262],{"class":247},"\"getCoupons\"",[39,264,265],{"class":239},")\n",[16,267,268],{},"這樣分頁邏輯就製作好了",[16,270,271],{},[208,272],{"alt":197,"src":273},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FuiDLWuM.png",[16,275,276],{},"並且也可以做切換頁動作",[16,278,279],{},[208,280],{"alt":281,"src":282},"切換頁動作","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FFcOZjFI.png",[12,284,285],{"id":285},"結尾",[16,287,288],{},"這邊有些人會覺得\"那就由後端製作就好了啦，幹嘛讓前端這麼辛苦\"，其實這方面要前後端做雙向溝通的，並不是全都由後端製作就好，經過分頁邏輯 1 & 2，你也了解到由製作分頁邏輯是多麻煩的事，雖然後端製作好往前端傳可以省很多事情，但是這部分是雙方一起溝通的唷~(自己寫過後端分頁邏輯，所以滿清楚的)",[290,291,292],"style",{},"html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html pre.shiki code .sj_SG, html code.shiki .sj_SG{--shiki-default:#DBB7FF}html pre.shiki code .sMAXC, html code.shiki .sMAXC{--shiki-default:#F0F3F6}html pre.shiki code .sWyjQ, html code.shiki .sWyjQ{--shiki-default:#FF9492}html pre.shiki code .sTRMh, html code.shiki .sTRMh{--shiki-default:#ADDCFF}",{"title":34,"searchDepth":48,"depth":48,"links":294},[295,296,297,298],{"id":14,"depth":48,"text":14},{"id":21,"depth":48,"text":21},{"id":197,"depth":48,"text":197},{"id":285,"depth":48,"text":285},"Vue","2019-07-29 16:17:31","md","zh-Hant",{},"\u002Fvue-!\u002Fvue-2","1",{"title":6,"description":18},false,"Vue 出一個女友吧!\u002FVue-出一個女友吧-製作分頁邏輯-2",[299,310],"Vue 出一個女友吧",null,"\u002Fvue\u002F20190729\u002F371929708\u002F","P8qsqRbUUKNAw3ZFxKKmiWtx3eH3M95uHW1kulJIQEs",{"newer":315,"older":319},{"url":316,"title":317,"date":318},"\u002Fvue\u002F20190729\u002F4147561982\u002F","Vue 出一